 quite The bottoms among the dunes have a dense vegetation as compared with that of the dunes themselves It Is characterized especially by the presence of a grama grass Bouteloua forming almost a turf and by frequent clumps of Ephedra of a grayish purple color at this season and with threescaled nodes These bottoms usually show no sign of moisture but In two places we found water holes the water so alkaline that the horses would not drink It at the end of their first days drive Probably the most extraordinary product of the Sonora desert west of Torres Mex UCSON has a cli mate of a thor oughly desert char acter and a flora including moun tains and plain rich In speciesand genera In addi tion to its situa tion in the heart of the desert of Arizona it is cen trally located both as to position and"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-09-04T23:18:58.490Z", "group": ["ndnp/ohi", "ohio-historical-society-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83035565/1910-09-29/ed-1/?sp=3", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_gann_ver01:data:sn83035565:00296026906:1910092901:0181/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=468&w=329", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_gann_ver01:data:sn83035565:00296026906:1910092901:0181/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=937&w=659", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ohi/batch_ohi_gann_ver01/data/sn83035565/00296026906/1910092901/0181.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "location": ["greenville", "darke", "ohio", "united states"], "location_city": ["greenville"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["darke"], "location_state": ["ohio"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["6", "0000000003", "1", "sn83035565", "0", "9", "2"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn